# Skill: meeting-notes

## Purpose
Capture structured meeting notes during or after a call.

## File naming

meeting-notes/YYYY-MM-DD-[short-title].md

## Format

# [MEETING TITLE]
**Date:** YYYY-MM-DD
**Attendees:** [list]
**Duration:** [X min]

## Summary
[2-3 sentences.]

## Decisions
- [decision]

## Action items
| Action | Owner | Due |
|---|---|---|

## Notes
[Freeform.]

## Follow-up
[Emails to send, invites to create, files to update.]

## After capturing

1. Add action items to tasks/current.md
2. Update any related project files
3. Offer to draft follow-up emails via email-drafter
